1557773.title: Brooklyn - Broadway - Grove Street (northwest corner)
1557773.folder: Brooklyn & Broadway & Grove Street (northwest corner), Brooklyn, NY

704723f-b.text:
(1)
Grove Strcet, east side, north of Broadway, showing property of Loftus Wood at No. 16-18 (the house with the porch). This property which was badly damaged by fire en September 22, 1924, does net appear
on the realty maps of 1929.
May 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
The same, another view. Loftus Wood was president of the Franklin Ave. R.R. Ce., now the Franklin Ave. Trolley line.
January 4, 1923.
Eugene L. Arruster Collection.
(3)
The same, another view.
1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
